		<div class="content1">
			<h1>Introduction</h1>
			<br>
			<hr>
			<div class="info1">
				<p>
				<ul>
					<li>Welcome to <span class="quick">Quickkart</span>, your
						one-stop destination for all your online shopping needs. Explore a
						vast and diverse range of products, from the latest electronics to
