			</div>
		</div>



		<section id="services-container">
			<h1 class="primary2">
				Why should you choose to shop with Quick<i
					class='bx bxs-shopping-bags bx-tada' style='color: #0058ff'></i>kart?
			</h1>
			<div id="services">
				<div class="box">
					<img src="img/mission.png">
					<h2 class="secondary">Our Mission</h2>
					<p>Our mission revolves around you, the customer. We are
						committed to delivering excellence by offering a carefully curated
						range of [products & categories] to your diverse needs. Our
						dedication to quality, affordability, and customer satisfaction is
						unwavering.</p>
				</div>
				<div class="box">
					<img src="img/image1.gif" width="230px">
					<h2 class="secondary">Join Us</h2>
					<p>We invite you to explore Quickkart and join us in this
